name: Medusa's Grateful Ending
description:
It was an alternate story of how Medusa's life went by. 
She was molested by a god, turning her into a monster. 
Then killed by Perseus, who only wants the trophy.
Kind of a tragic and heart breaking tale for such innocent pure soul like Medusa.

She doesn't deserve this kind of life. She deserves a better passing. 
So I decide to give her one. 
An alternate ending where she was not a trophy. 
Where she could choose her own way to die, 
petrified and welcoming a better ending :')
